net.wequick.small

Class AssetBundleLauncher

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.wequick.small.BundleLauncher
      • net.wequick.small.SoBundleLauncher
        • net.wequick.small.AssetBundleLauncher
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    WebBundleLauncher

    public abstract class AssetBundleLauncher
extends SoBundleLauncher
    This class launch the plugin asset by it's file name with an internal activity.

    This class resolve the bundle who's pkg is specified as "*.[neither app nor lib].*" in bundle.json.

    The internal activity parse the asset file and display it.
